41
00:03:41.880 --> 00:03:44.440
What time do you think we'll be able to go home?

42
00:03:44.440 --> 00:03:46.100
Xiao Nai, there's a package for Fang Si.

43
00:03:46.100 --> 00:03:49.600
Oh, coming! Amy, get your boyfriend to hurry up.

44
00:03:49.600 --> 00:03:51.700
