Hello? The reception isn't good. I can't hear you.

62
00:05:19.960 --> 00:05:22.080
Hello?

63
00:05:40.110 --> 00:05:42.720
How about I contact other modeling agencies

64
00:05:42.720 --> 00:05:45.440
and find someone to stand in for a while?

65
00:05:46.400 --> 00:05:49.160
If not, what about any of our colleagues?

66
00:05:49.160 --> 00:05:51.820
After all, it's only an advertising photoshoot today.

67
00:05:51.820 --> 00:05:53.560
It should not--

68
00:05:53.560 --> 00:05:56.220
Prepare the sample garments.

69
00:05:56.220 --> 00:06:00.340
Sample garments. Now. Immediately.

70
00:06:00.340 --> 00:06:02.680
Oh, okay.

71
00:06:07.840 --> 00:06:13.100
Fang Si, the Tang Huang CEO is here. He even brought the contract this time.

72
00:06:13.100 --> 00:06:15.220
Today's model is your boyfriend?

73
00:06:15.220 --> 00:06:17.020
Oh, yes.

74
00:06:17.020 --> 00:06:19.060
It's not his fault that the flight was delayed.

75
00:06:19.060 --> 00:06:22.380
And today is only an advertising photoshoot. Tomorrow's show is the most important.

76
00:06:22.380 --> 00:06:24.080
He has already landed. He'll be here soon.

77
00:06:24.080 --> 00:06:27.860
You can tell him not to come anymore. From the airport to here, even if there isn't much traffic,

78
00:06:27.860 --> 00:06:29.740
it'll take at least an hour.

79
00:06:29.740 --> 00:06:32.840
But he specifically flew here for this photoshoot.

80
00:06:32.840 --> 00:06:36.560
Anyway, it isn't his fault. We're only having an advertising photoshoot today.

81
00:06:36.560 --> 00:06:38.480
Aren't we?

82
00:07:09.380 --> 00:07:12.980
Don Juan - Tang Huang Fashion

83
00:07:12.980 --> 00:07:14.860
I am confident that my life will be brilliant.

84
00:07:15.740 --> 00:07:17.620
What are you thinking of?

85
00:07:17.620 --> 00:07:20.600
You look so distracted.

86
00:07:20.600 --> 00:07:24.360
What else do you think I'll be thinking of?

87
00:07:24.360 --> 00:07:26.640
Have you missed me?

88
00:07:29.020 --> 00:07:33.600
Are you done with your tantrums yet? I've especially made a trip here and you're still going on about  it?

89
00:07:37.420 --> 00:07:41.340
I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I really didn't see you.

90
00:07:41.340 --> 00:07:43.560
I really didn't see you.

91
00:07:45.760 --> 00:07:49.220
He didn't do it on purpose, either. There was no harm done, anyway. Let it go. Don't be angry.

92
00:07:49.220 --> 00:07:51.820
I'm really sorry. I can pay for the dry cleaning.

93
00:07:51.820 --> 00:07:54.380
You having a quarrel?

94
00:07:54.380 --> 00:07:57.560
She's a lot to handle, isn't she?

95
00:07:57.560 --> 00:07:59.360
What has it got to do with me?

96
00:08:08.900 --> 00:08:12.580
Look at this scarf he was wearing. What poor taste.

97
00:08:15.100 --> 00:08:17.800
Let it go. Today's a special day, isn't it?

98
00:08:17.800 --> 00:08:21.140
He already got a scolding from you. His heart is...

99
00:08:21.140 --> 00:08:22.840
Is probably bleeding now.

100
00:08:22.840 --> 00:08:25.740
Who in this world would really die if someone left another person?

101
00:08:25.740 --> 00:08:31.300
When darkness comes, even your shadow will leave you. So when you're living life, you can only depend on yourself. Does this look nice?

102
00:08:31.700 --> 00:08:34.040
It looks okay, I guess.

103
00:08:34.040 --> 00:08:36.260
You're laughing?

104
00:08:36.260 --> 00:08:38.860
- How are you?
- I'm good. I'm great.

105
00:08:38.860 --> 00:08:42.580
I'm good as long as I can see you. Here, let me do a spin for you.

106
00:08:44.120 --> 00:08:48.700
It's best when you're back. I'm all good as long as I can see you.

107
00:08:48.700 --> 00:08:50.820
Then I'm not angry anymore.

108
00:08:50.820 --> 00:08:53.340
You're driving?

109
00:08:53.340 --> 00:08:56.100
I'll drive! You drive tomorrow.

110
00:08:56.100 --> 00:09:00.060
- Then what about the day after?
- Me.

111
00:09:10.900 --> 00:09:13.200
Fang Si, the new contract has been drawn up.

112
00:09:13.200 --> 00:09:16.040
- Xiao Nai, how is it?
- What do you think of this?

113
00:09:16.040 --> 00:09:18.320
Let's go with this then.

114
00:09:18.320 --> 00:09:22.780
Director Luo, I've said it before. I will never work with Tang Huang.

115
00:09:22.780 --> 00:09:27.440
We're really sincere about this cooperation. Look at me, a director and yet I've made so many trips here.

116
00:09:27.440 --> 00:09:32.100
On top of that, a small workshop like yours, being able to work with Tang Huang is a good opportunity for you, too.

117
00:09:32.100 --> 00:09:34.920
We've already changed the terms of the contract for you. Do you want to have a look at it?

118
00:09:34.920 --> 00:09:36.920
Are you scared?

119
00:09:36.920 --> 00:09:39.760
What do I have to be scared of?

120
00:09:39.760 --> 00:09:41.220
Afraid that you'll eat me up?

121
00:09:41.220 --> 00:09:44.660
Tomorrow, Qiao Rui Si Group will be holding a joint brands audition.

122
00:09:44.660 --> 00:09:47.940
All the fashion brands in the country will be taking part.

123
00:09:47.940 --> 00:09:52.160
I believe Tang Huang would cherish this opportunity as well. The sample is good to go.

124
00:09:53.380 --> 00:09:57.580
At this time, you're so insistent on working with me to acquire my brand.

125
00:09:57.580 --> 00:09:59.480
You're afraid that Fancy will snatch your spotlight, aren't you?

126
00:09:59.480 --> 00:10:01.660
Fang Si, you can't say it like that.

127
00:10:01.660 --> 00:10:05.300
I say, you newcomers really don't know the industry well.

128
00:10:05.300 --> 00:10:10.980
I know that Qiao Rui Si Group has not accepted your application to participate.

129
00:10:10.980 --> 00:10:15.540
So, you can have two different choices, isn't it?

130
00:10:17.280 --> 00:10:21.020
Director Luo, I appreciate your kind gesture.

131
00:10:21.020 --> 00:10:23.760
I'll see you at the audition tomorrow.

132
00:10:23.760 --> 00:10:25.540
I won't send you out.

133
00:10:30.840 --> 00:10:34.580
Xiao Nai, confirm this final draft.

134
00:10:34.580 --> 00:10:38.100
Fang Si, my boyfriend says he'll be here now, immediately. There will be absolutely no problem.

135
00:10:38.100 --> 00:10:40.940
Saying, "Absolutely no problem," in itself is already a problem.

136
00:10:40.940 --> 00:10:42.520
Why not wait for ten more minutes?

137
00:10:42.520 --> 00:10:45.900
- We're not prepared here, either.
- Send a lawyer's letter to his management agency.

138
00:10:45.900 --> 00:10:48.000
Sue him for breaching the contract.

139
00:10:49.720 --> 00:10:51.680
Who is she?

140
00:10:51.680 --> 00:10:54.120
Amy, Fang Si is just saying...

141
00:10:54.120 --> 00:10:56.820
- She won't really sue your boyfriend.
- Who knows?

142
00:10:56.820 --> 00:11:00.880
On top of being a weekend, today's Valentines' Day, too. She can't get married and she's dragging us down, too.

143
00:11:00.880 --> 00:11:03.240
For her own dreams, she doesn't even care about our feelings.

144
00:11:03.240 --> 00:11:05.480
Let's not talk about it anymore. We should be preparing now.

145
00:11:05.480 --> 00:11:07.200
Amy, let's get ready to set off soon.

146
00:11:07.200 --> 00:11:09.320
What are you doing? You need me for an advertising photoshoot, too?

147
00:11:09.320 --> 00:11:12.680
Princess, I'm begging you. Don't be angry.

148
00:11:12.680 --> 00:11:15.460
Just endure her for a while.

149
00:11:21.360 --> 00:11:25.980
I thought you opening a restaurant was just for fun.

150
00:11:25.980 --> 00:11:28.320
Who would have thought...

151
00:11:29.760 --> 00:11:31.620
it would be this good.

152
00:11:31.620 --> 00:11:36.680
How is it? My capabilities are better than just endorsing Tang Huang right?

153
00:11:36.680 --> 00:11:39.960
Looks like I've really underestimated you.

154
00:11:39.960 --> 00:11:44.020
Anyway, what I like best is endorsing for Tang Huang.

155
00:11:44.020 --> 00:11:46.820
And I've decided, not only in this lifetime,

156
00:11:46.820 --> 00:11:48.340
I'll endorse Tang Huang in my next lifetime, too.

157
00:11:48.340 --> 00:11:50.600
Please pardon me in the next lifetime.

158
00:11:50.600 --> 00:11:53.100
What do you mean by that?

159
00:11:56.380 --> 00:12:01.100
But seriously, the furniture here really does look classy.

160
00:12:01.100 --> 00:12:04.200
That's because I listened to you. You said so yourself.

161
00:12:04.200 --> 00:12:07.140
Life is meant to be appreciated slowly, right?

162
00:12:07.140 --> 00:12:09.380
We need to enjoy it.

163
00:12:09.380 --> 00:12:12.680
Then we shouldn't pass our lives as though we're in a war, should we?

164
00:12:12.680 --> 00:12:15.000
Wait for me.

165
00:12:18.600 --> 00:12:21.720
Fancy

166
00:12:21.720 --> 00:12:24.860
What a weird customer. You haven't taken your medicine, right?

167
00:12:24.860 --> 00:12:29.040
I think he has to take a lot of medicine to be able to recover.

168
00:12:29.040 --> 00:12:33.240
So aren't you the happiest when you're with me?

169
00:12:36.520 --> 00:12:38.900
Let's go. Dinner's ready.

170
00:12:42.960 --> 00:12:47.140
Let me introduce this to you. This is called low-heat salmon.

171
00:12:47.140 --> 00:12:50.920
Because you don't like things that are too dry, so I learned this cooking method.

172
00:12:50.920 --> 00:12:56.440
It allows you to taste the freshness of the fish even though it's cooked.

173
00:12:58.720 --> 00:13:00.540
How is it?

174
00:13:05.700 --> 00:13:07.360
It's delicious.

175
00:13:08.140 --> 00:13:09.780
I'm all embarrassed.

176
00:13:09.780 --> 00:13:11.940
It's fragrant and it's tender.

177
00:13:11.940 --> 00:13:14.160
Eat slowly.

178
00:13:14.160 --> 00:13:18.520
Didn't you say life is meant to be appreciated slowly? You're eating so fast.

179
00:13:18.520 --> 00:13:19.840
How do you appreciate the taste?

180
00:13:19.840 --> 00:13:22.400
You only need to slowly taste food that doesn't taste nice,

181
00:13:22.400 --> 00:13:25.260
because then you can slowly finish your food

182
00:13:25.260 --> 00:13:28.760
so you can eat less of it. But this really tastes heavenly.

183
00:13:28.760 --> 00:13:30.440
See, it's all gone now.

184
00:13:30.440 --> 00:13:32.320
Here, more for you.

185
00:13:32.320 --> 00:13:36.040
- Luckily you can sweet talk!
- It is delicious!

186
00:13:39.300 --> 00:13:42.940
I told you to eat slowly. Don't choke.

187
00:13:43.800 --> 00:13:48.260
We'll work after your meal. Come and look for me when you are done.

188
00:13:56.820 --> 00:13:58.880
Hurry up.

189
00:14:08.340 --> 00:14:12.720
Have you known any new girl when you were overseas?

190
00:14:13.720 --> 00:14:15.720
Of course,

191
00:14:18.180 --> 00:14:20.020
not.

192
00:14:20.020 --> 00:14:23.980
You were always calling me three times a day during my meal times. Do you think I would have had the time?

193
00:14:23.980 --> 00:14:25.800
Still giving me a black face!

194
00:14:25.800 --> 00:14:29.160
But you haven't changed your eating habits!

195
00:14:29.160 --> 00:14:32.600
So other habits must be even harder to change.

196
00:14:32.600 --> 00:14:35.100
We have already been together for so many years.

197
00:14:35.100 --> 00:14:40.800
My Lady, I have even travelled from afar to celebrate

198
00:14:40.800 --> 00:14:45.520
Valentine's Day with you. What is there to worry about?

199
00:14:55.840 --> 00:14:58.000
Okay.

200
00:14:59.480 --> 00:15:00.520
Hello.

201
00:15:00.520 --> 00:15:05.620
President Fu, I am here because of your reputation to save today's situation.

202
00:15:05.620 --> 00:15:08.280
I won't accept anything less than $2000.

203
00:15:08.280 --> 00:15:10.100
Bring the reflector.

204
00:15:15.060 --> 00:15:24.980
