- so you must be careful in the future.
- Thanks, Big Brother.

212
00:15:58.960 --> 00:16:01.140
You are welcome.

213
00:16:04.320 --> 00:16:06.660
Then I will leave first.  You be careful.

214
00:16:06.660 --> 00:16:09.520
- Goodbye.
- Goodbye.

215
00:16:11.640 --> 00:16:15.420
Don't do that. President Fu, why aren't you taking anymore photos?

216
00:16:15.420 --> 00:16:19.860
- What do you mean by this, President Fu? You called me over, yet you're not taking pictures anymore?
- Wait! Wait!

217
00:16:19.860 --> 00:16:22.360
- Is there a problem?
- Do you have time?

218
00:16:22.360 --> 00:16:24.140
I would like to ask for your help.

219
00:16:24.140 --> 00:16:28.060
Help? How do I know that you are not a fraud?

220
00:16:28.660 --> 00:16:32.040
Be my model. $3000 an hour.

221
00:16:32.040 --> 00:16:36.620
$3000 an hour? You sound more like a fraud.

222
00:16:36.620 --> 00:16:39.060
So you agree?

223
00:16:41.640 --> 00:16:44.620
How is it? Can you do it?

224
00:16:45.260 --> 00:16:48.420
I am sorry but I am not interested.

225
00:16:50.880 --> 00:16:54.760
What is this? You got me in a hurry and now you are looking for someone else!

226
00:16:54.760 --> 00:16:59.900
I have already told you. I will charge you once I am out of the office. So regardless, you must still pay for my time.

227
00:16:59.900 --> 00:17:02.860
You can't even pass the advertising photoshoot, yet you still dare to ask me for money?

228
00:17:02.860 --> 00:17:05.380
It's not bad to give $100 for your transportation cost.

229
00:17:05.380 --> 00:17:08.400
Go ask Xiao Nai for the money, then quickly be on your way.

230
00:17:08.400 --> 00:17:10.920
Our model has arrived.

231
00:17:10.920 --> 00:17:13.300
Sorry I was late. So it was you!

232
00:17:13.300 --> 00:17:15.560
Then why did President Fu bother looking for me?

233
00:17:15.560 --> 00:17:17.140
How would I know why?

234
00:17:17.140 --> 00:17:19.560
She always thinks too highly of herself and likes to order people around.

235
00:17:19.560 --> 00:17:21.320
What's wrong?

236
00:17:21.320 --> 00:17:24.330
Why did you arrive so late?

237
00:17:26.700 --> 00:17:31.800
How about after the shoot, I will help you with your work and I will still pay you?

238
00:17:31.800 --> 00:17:33.620
You help me with my work?

239
00:17:33.620 --> 00:17:36.320
Are you super woman or Doraemon?

240
00:17:36.320 --> 00:17:40.560
Sorry. I am really in a hurry.  I don't have time to play with you.

241
00:17:44.260 --> 00:17:46.340
Listen to me.

242
00:17:46.340 --> 00:17:47.600
